where it's just there to be visually perceived.

1306
01:01:53,410 --> 01:01:56,870
另一方面 就是和我们的行动有关了
And on the other side, a performance kind of action.

1307
01:01:57,960 --> 01:01:59,570
看上去很有趣吧
It looks like a lot of fun,

1308
01:01:59,570 --> 01:02:01,840
