01:07:27,040 --> 01:07:29,580
在新泽西州的樱桃山的耶鲁学校里
At the Yale School in Cherry Hill, New Jersey,

1428
01:07:29,670 --> 01:07:32,540
孩子们通过乐高积木在与彼此交流
kids are interacting with each other, playing with LEGO bricks.

